    <item>
      <title>由于贷款规则草案可能受到影响，印度银行股面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/bank-stocks-under-pressure-in-india-as-draft-loan-rules-may-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度银行已成为该国股市的一大风险来源，此前，拟议的规则可能会提高支持某些项目的贷款拨备，导致最近出现抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/bank-stocks-under-pressure-in-india-as-draft-loan-rules-may-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 06:49:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度航空低成本航空公司因机组人员请病假取消航班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/air-india-s-low-cost-unit-cancels-flights-as-crew-call-in-sick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据追踪公司 FlightAware 的数据，由于机组人员集体请病假，印度航空有限公司旗下的廉价航空公司自周二以来取消了近 30 个航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/air-india-s-low-cost-unit-cancels-flights-as-crew-call-in-sick</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 06:33:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利工业在短暂回升后萎缩幅度超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hungary-industry-shrinks-more-than-expected-after-brief-upswing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三的数据显示，匈牙利的工业正在努力复苏，国内消费部门将推动增长并为公共财政提供急需的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hungary-industry-shrinks-more-than-expected-after-brief-upswing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 06:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
