      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-industrial-production-shrinks-for-first-time-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国工业产出今年首次下降——突显了该行业在欧洲最大经济体中面临的持久挑战。]]></description>
